Right, right, right.

00:29:42.470 --> 00:29:46.020
Sometimes, some of the foods
have been donated by the local

00:29:46.020 --> 00:29:48.080
community there, but
it is not enough.

00:29:48.080 --> 00:29:52.240
For that amount of children, you
need some donations from

00:29:52.240 --> 00:29:54.560
local community, as well as
from foreign countries.

00:29:54.560 --> 00:29:59.620
But now, some of the wiser
orphans and children are

00:29:59.620 --> 00:30:02.120
